      *
      * Currency File
     FSDCURRL1IF  E           K        DISK
     F                                              KINFSR *PSSR
      *
      * Bank File
     FSDBANKL0IF  E           K        DISK
     F                                              KINFSR *PSSR
      *
      * Exposure Management Sub-Line File
     FEMTFSLL0IF  E           K        DISK
     F                                              KINFSR *PSSR
      *
      * Exposure Management Sub-Line Account File
     FEMTFSAL1IF  E           K        DISK
     F                                              KINFSR *PSSR
      *
