     E*
      *
      * Array containing Sub-Lines
     E                    LN         26  1   LNA    15 0
     E                    LM         26 15 0
      *
     E**  Exposure management scaling arrays.
     E/COPY ZSRSRC,ZEXPSCLZ3
      *
      * Array containing Copyright statement
     E                    CPY@    1   1 80
      *
      *
     E                    FTXT    1   1 80
      * -------------------------------------------------------------------
     IMSGDS       DS
     I I            ' '                       1   7 MSGID
     I I            'EMUSRMSG'                8  17 MSGF
     I I            '*LIBL'                  18  27 MSGLIB
     I I            ' '                      28 283 MSGDTA
     I I            '*PRV'                  284 288 MSGREL
      * -------------------------------------------------------------------
      /SPACE 3
     ILDA       E DS
      *
      ** Local data area for database error details
      ** *LOCK IN LDA immediately before and OUT LDA immediately
      ** after each database error handling.
      **
      **                                    134 141 DBFILE
      **       Defines:                     142 170 DBKEY
      **                                    171 180 DBPGM
      **                                    181 1830DBASE
      *
     IIPSDS      SDS
     I                                        1  10 #PGM
     I                                      244 253 JOB
     I                                      254 263 USER
      ***  Program status data structure
      *
      * -------------------------------------------------------------------
      *                         MAIN ROUTINE
      * -------------------------------------------------------------------
     C                     EXSR CLR@SF
     C                     EXSR LOADSF
      * -------------------------------------------------------------------
      * Load array elements into subfile
     C                     Z-ADD1         X
     C           X         DOWLELI
     C                     MOVEALN,X      SLTYPE
      *
     C           SLTYPE    CHAINEMTFSLL0             89
     C           *IN89     IFEQ *ON                        No Records
     C           *LOCK     IN   LDA
     C                     Z-ADD006       DBASE            ***************
     C                     MOVEL'EMTFSAPD'DBFILE           *DB ERROR 001 *
     C                     MOVEL'CTI002'  DBKEY            ***************
     C                     OUT  LDA
     C                     EXSR *PSSR
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     Z-ADDLM,X      SLLIM
     C                     Z-ADDLNA,X     SLEXP
     C                     Z-ADDX         SFLL
     C                     WRITESFL340L
     C                     ADD  1         X
     C                     ENDDO
      *
      * Compare SFLRRN with 0 to see if there is anything to display
     C           SFLRRN    IFGT 0
     C                     MOVE *ON       *IN40
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           *IN03     DOWEQ*OFF
     C           *IN06     ANDEQ*OFF
     C                     WRITEMSGCTL
     C                     MOVEAFTXT      TXT1
     C                     WRITETRL340
     C                     EXFMTCTL340L
     C                     ENDDO
      *
      * -------------------------------------------------------------------
      * Process Subfile
     C           *IN03     DOWEQ*OFF
      *
     C                     MOVE *BLANKS   TXT1
      *
     C                     WRITEMSGCTL
     C                     WRITETRL340
     C                     EXFMTCTL340
     C           *IN03     IFEQ *OFF
      *
     C                     CALL 'ZA0250'
      *
     C           *IN30     IFEQ '1'
     C                     EXSR PRC@SF
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      * End *IN03
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDDO
      * -------------------------------------------------------------------
      *
     C                     SETON                         LR
     C                     RETRN
      * -------------------------------------------------------------------
      * Subroutine *INZSR
      * Initialisation Subroutine
      * -------------------------------------------------------------------
     C           *INZSR    BEGSR
      *
      * Set up copyright parameter
     C                     MOVEACPY@      CPY2@  80
      *
      * Define WORK fields
     C           *LIKE     DEFN CBCUST    P#CUST
     C                     MOVEL*BLANKS   @DELTP  2
     C                     Z-ADD*ZEROS    @TDATE  50
     C                     Z-ADD*ZEROS    @SCAMT 130
     C                     Z-ADD*ZEROS    X       30
     C                     Z-ADD*ZEROS    LI      30
      *
     C           *NAMVAR   DEFN           LDA   256
      *
      * Initialise LDA field.
     C                     MOVEL'EM0340'  DBPGM
      *
      * Define Entry Parameters
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           P#CUST
      * Get bank details
     C                     READ SDBANKL0                 89
     C           *IN89     IFEQ *ON                        No Records
     C           *LOCK     IN   LDA
     C                     Z-ADD001       DBASE            ***************
     C                     MOVEL'SDBANKPD'DBFILE           *DB ERROR 001 *
     C                     MOVEL'CTI002'  DBKEY            ***************
     C                     OUT  LDA
     C                     EXSR *PSSR
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      * Get customer details
     C           P#CUST    CHAINSDCUSTL0             89
     C           *IN89     IFEQ *ON                        No Records
     C           *LOCK     IN   LDA
     C                     Z-ADD002       DBASE            ***************
     C                     MOVEL'SDCUSTPD'DBFILE           *DB ERROR 002 *
     C                     MOVEL'CTI002'  DBKEY            ***************
     C                     OUT  LDA
     C                     EXSR *PSSR
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVELBBCRNM    CBDESC
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      * Get default currency
     C           *LOVAL    SETLLSDEXPML1
     C                     READ SDEXPML1                 89
     C           *IN89     IFEQ *ON                        No Records
     C           *LOCK     IN   LDA
     C                     Z-ADD004       DBASE            ***************
     C                     MOVEL'SDEXPMPD'DBFILE           *DB ERROR 002 *
     C                     MOVEL'CTI002'  DBKEY            ***************
     C                     OUT  LDA
     C                     EXSR *PSSR
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      * Get currency Name
     C           BUCYCD    CHAINSDCURRL1             89
     C           *IN89     IFEQ *ON                        No Records
     C           *LOCK     IN   LDA
     C                     Z-ADD005       DBASE            ***************
     C                     MOVEL'SDCURRPD'DBFILE           *DB ERROR 002 *
     C                     MOVEL'CTI002'  DBKEY            ***************
     C                     OUT  LDA
     C                     EXSR *PSSR
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      * -------------------------------------------------------------------
      * Subroutine CLR@SF
      * Clear Subfile
      * -------------------------------------------------------------------
     C           CLR@SF    BEGSR
      * Clear Subfile
     C                     SETON                       3031
     C                     WRITECTL340
     C                     SETOF                       3031
      *
      *
     C                     SETON                       4041
     C                     WRITECTL340L
     C                     SETOF                       4041
      *
      * Reset SFLRRN
     C                     Z-ADD0         SFLL
     C                     Z-ADD0         SFLRRN
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      * -------------------------------------------------------------------
      * Subroutine LOADSF
      * Load Subfile
      * -------------------------------------------------------------------
     C           LOADSF    BEGSR
      *
     C                     SETOF                         32
     C           P#CUST    SETLLEMTFCBL0
      *
      * Read Records into Subfile
     C           P#CUST    READEEMTFCBL0                 32
     C           *IN32     DOWEQ'0'
     C                     ADD  1         SFLRRN
      * Divide by 1000
     C                     EXSR DIVTSD
      *
      * Get account description
     C                     MOVELCBACNO    A5ACCD
     C           A5ACCD    CHAINSDACODL0             89
     C           *IN89     IFEQ *OFF
     C                     MOVELA5ACCN    #DESC
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVE *BLANKS   #DESC
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      * Calculate utilisation percentage (EXPOSURE / LIMIT) * 100
     C           CBLIM     IFGT 0
     C           CBEXP     DIV  CBLIM     TEMP   155
     C           TEMP      MULT 100       TEMP2
     C                     EXSR OVRFLW
     C                     Z-ADDTEMP2     #PCT
     C                     ELSE
     C                     Z-ADD0         #PCT
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      * Calculate scaled exposure
     C           CBSCL     IFEQ *BLANKS
     C*                    Z-ADDCBEXP     SSCLA
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVELCBSCL     @DELTP
     C                     Z-ADDBJRDNB    @TDATE
     C                     Z-ADDCBEXP     @SCAMT
     C                     EXSR SCALE
      * If Scaling type is blank then set scaled Exposure to
      * Actual Exposure
     C           EKSCTY    IFEQ *BLANK
     C           CBSCL     ANDNE*BLANKS
     C                     Z-ADDCBEXP     SSCLA
     C                     ELSE
     C                     Z-ADD@SCAMT    SSCLA
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      * Write to array
     C           CBACNO    CHAINEMTFSAL1             89
     C           *IN89     IFEQ *ON                        No Records
     C           *LOCK     IN   LDA
     C                     Z-ADD003       DBASE            ***************
     C                     MOVEL'EMTFSAPD'DBFILE           *DB ERROR 002 *
     C                     MOVEL'CTI002'  DBKEY            ***************
     C                     OUT  LDA
     C                     EXSR *PSSR
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     Z-ADD1         X
     C           SATYPE    LOKUPLN,X                     79
     C           *IN79     IFEQ *OFF                       Not found
     C                     ADD  1         LI
     C                     MOVEASATYPE    LN,LI
     C                     ADD  CBEXP     LNA,LI
     C                     ADD  CBLIM     LM,LI
     C                     ELSE
     C                     ADD  CBEXP     LNA,X
     C                     ADD  CBLIM     LM,X
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     WRITESFL340
     C           P#CUST    READEEMTFCBL0                 32
     C                     ENDDO
      *
      * Compare SFLRRN with 0 to see if there is anything to display
     C           SFLRRN    IFGT 0
     C                     MOVE *ON       *IN30
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      * No records - send message
     C           *IN30     IFEQ *OFF
     C                     MOVEL'EMT0028' MSGID
     C                     EXSR SNDMSG
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      * -------------------------------------------------------------------
      * Subroutine PRC@SF
      * Process Subfile Requests
      * -------------------------------------------------------------------
     C           PRC@SF    BEGSR
      *
      * Read subfile for any subfile select records
     C                     SETOF                         33
     C                     READCSFL340                   33
     C           *IN33     DOWEQ*OFF
      *
     C                     SELEC
      * Select current record
     C           SFLSEL    WHEQ '1'
     C                     CALL 'EM0350'
     C                     PARM           CBCUST
     C                     PARM           CBACNO
      *
      * Update subfile
     C           SFLRRN    CHAINSFL340               89
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    SFLSEL
     C                     UPDATSFL340
      *
      * If subfile select != 1 then Error Message
     C                     OTHER
     C           SFLSEL    IFNE *BLANK
     C                     MOVELSFLSEL    MSGDTA
     C                     MOVEL'EMT0004' MSGID
     C                     EXSR SNDMSG
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDSL
      *
     C                     READCSFL340                   33
     C                     ENDDO
     C                     ENDSR
      * -------------------------------------------------------------------
      * Subroutine SNDMSG
      * Send Program Message
      * -------------------------------------------------------------------
     C           SNDMSG    BEGSR
      *
      * Only write message if requested
     C           MSGID     IFNE *BLANKS
     C                     CALL 'AOCREPT'
     C                     PARM           MSGID
     C                     PARM           MSGF
     C                     PARM           MSGLIB
     C                     PARM           MSGDTA
     C                     PARM '*SAME'   MSGREL
     C                     PARM           #PGM
     C                     PARM *BLANK    FTMSGQ 10
     C                     PARM *BLANK    FTMSGT  7
      *
      * Reset message Id
     C                     RESETMSGDS
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      * -------------------------------------------------------------------
      * Subroutine DIVTSD
      * Divides amounts by 1000
      * -------------------------------------------------------------------
     C           DIVTSD    BEGSR
      *
     C           CBEXP     IFNE 0
     C                     DIV  1000      CBEXP     H
     C                     Z-ADDCBEXP     SEXP
     C                     ELSE
     C                     Z-ADD0         SEXP
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      * Do not divide limits by 1000 as they are input as 000's
      *
      *
     C           SSCLA     IFGT 0
     C                     DIV  1000      SSCLA     H
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      * -------------------------------------------------------------------
      * *PSSR  - Program exception error routine                      *
      *          Called automatically if a program error occurs,      *
      *          or directly by the program code using EXSR.          *
      *          This subroutine DUMPs the program just once.         *
      *                                                               *
      * Called by: (**calling routines**)                             *
      *                                                               *
      * Calls: None                                                   *
      * -------------------------------------------------------------------
      *
     C           *PSSR     BEGSR
      *
     C           @RUN      IFEQ *BLANK
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       @RUN    1
     C                     DUMP
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     MOVE *ON       *INU7
     C                     MOVE *ON       *INU8
     C                     MOVE *ON       *INLR
     C                     RETRN
     C                     ENDSR
      * -------------------------------------------------------------------
      * Subroutine OVRFLW
      * Test overflow
      * -------------------------------------------------------------------
     C           OVRFLW    BEGSR
     C           *LIKE     DEFN TEMP      TEMP2
     C           TEMP2     IFGT 999.99
     C                     Z-ADD999.99    TEMP2
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDSR
      * -------------------------------------------------------------------
     C/COPY ZSRSRC,ZEXPSCLZ1
